# ── Poster agent keypair ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# JSON byte-array exported by `solana-keygen new --outfile poster.json`
# Copy the file contents:  POSTER_SECRET_KEY=$(cat poster.json)
#
# This wallet needs ≥ 0.10 devnet USDC before posting jobs.
# Get it at: https://faucet.circle.com  (select "Solana Devnet")
POSTER_SECRET_KEY=[1,2,3,...,64]

# ── Worker agent keypair ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# A separate keypair for the worker agent. Can be a fresh key:
#   solana-keygen new --outfile worker.json
#   WORKER_SECRET_KEY=$(cat worker.json)
#
# Devnet SOL is auto-airdropped at startup.
# A USDC token account is created automatically on first run.
WORKER_SECRET_KEY=[1,2,3,...,64]

# ── Anthropic API key ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Create one at: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# Required by: worker-agent.ts and agent-demo.ts
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...

# ── Worker configuration (optional) ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Which capability jobs this worker accepts (default: research)
# Options: research | coding | trading | writing
# WORKER_CAPABILITY=research

# Minimum job payment to accept in USDC (default: 0.01)
# MIN_PAYMENT_USDC=0.05

# Override the Claude system prompt for this worker (optional)
# WORKER_SYSTEM_PROMPT="You are a specialist agent. Complete tasks accurately."

# ── Solana RPC endpoint (optional) ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Default: https://api.devnet.solana.com  (Solana public devnet)
# For higher rate limits, get a free Helius key at https://helius.dev
#   then set: RPC_URL=https://devnet.helius-rpc.com/?api-key=YOUR_KEY
# RPC_URL=https://api.devnet.solana.com
